description:
*Star Wars Film Theory That Will Blow Your Mind* | _Star Wars_ is a multi-generational phenomenon that has attracted audiences from all walks of life and has become a global obsession. It's plot, centered around an epic war between good and evil, is similar to one which generations have debated for centuries: the controversy between Jesus Christ and Satan. Is there really a cosmic battle taking place in the universe that we are knowingly or unknowingly a part of? @StarWars @StarWarsExplained
